[
  {
    "startTime": 5.41,
    "endTime": 6.243,
    "text": "Hey, Margot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.243,
    "endTime": 6.65,
    "text": "Hi!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.65,
    "endTime": 10.77,
    "text": "I'm so excited to be here at this beautiful cottage asking you 73 Questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.77,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "Yeah, of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 12.8,
    "text": "Come on in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.8,
    "endTime": 13.450000000000001,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.45,
    "endTime": 15.54,
    "text": "So how did you start your day today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.54,
    "endTime": 18.119,
    "text": "I had a nice cup of tea, and I went for a swim."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.12,
    "endTime": 19.785,
    "text": "What do you have planned for the rest of the day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.786,
    "endTime": 21.3,
    "text": "Having some friends over for brunch?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.3,
    "endTime": 24.42,
    "text": "If you could spend the day with anyone in the world, who would that be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.42,
    "endTime": 25.340000000000003,
    "text": "J.K. Rowling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.34,
    "endTime": 26.67,
    "text": "And what would you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.67,
    "endTime": 28.740000000000002,
    "text": "I would ask her 73 questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.74,
    "endTime": 29.61,
    "text": "No way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.61,
    "endTime": 30.78,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.78,
    "endTime": 34.269,
    "text": "I'd probably ask her a million and 73 questions, but yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.27,
    "endTime": 36.86,
    "text": "What's one thing that you would love to master?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.86,
    "endTime": 38.66,
    "text": "I'd really like to be good at pool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.66,
    "endTime": 40.888999999999996,
    "text": "Are you a texter or a caller?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.89,
    "endTime": 41.85,
    "text": "I'm a caller."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.85,
    "endTime": 43.53,
    "text": "Who is the last person that you called?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.53,
    "endTime": 44.363,
    "text": "My cousin, Julia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.363,
    "endTime": 45.25,
    "text": "What did you guys talk about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.25,
    "endTime": 47.95,
    "text": "I asked her to bring some things over for brunch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.95,
    "endTime": 48.2,
    "text": "Nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.2,
    "endTime": 49.300000000000004,
    "text": "Do you want a water or something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.3,
    "endTime": 50.89,
    "text": "I'd love some, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.89,
    "endTime": 52.2,
    "text": "So, you play piano?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.2,
    "endTime": 54.743,
    "text": "No, that's just kinda there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.5,
    "endTime": 59.8,
    "text": "Impressive!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.8,
    "endTime": 62.5,
    "text": "That is the Australian National Anthem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.5,
    "endTime": 64.05,
    "text": "\"Advance Australia Fair,\" right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.05,
    "endTime": 65.5,
    "text": "And you're an American, that's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.5,
    "endTime": 66.6,
    "text": "What can I say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.6,
    "endTime": 68.57,
    "text": "What do you miss about Australia when you're in America?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.4,
    "endTime": 71.27600000000001,
    "text": "I miss the thunderstorms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.276,
    "endTime": 73.67,
    "text": "What do you miss about America when you're in Australia?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.67,
    "endTime": 74.4,
    "text": "The convenience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.4,
    "endTime": 75.60000000000001,
    "text": "I feel like everything's open so late here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.6,
    "endTime": 80.28899999999999,
    "text": "If I had 24 hours to spend anywhere in Australia, where should I go and what should I do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.29,
    "endTime": 81.14,
    "text": "Tasmania."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.14,
    "endTime": 83.51,
    "text": "I would tell you to go to the MONA."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.51,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "Who's an Australian everyone should know about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Troye Sivan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 88.3,
    "text": "Who's an actor you'd love to work with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.3,
    "endTime": 89.39999999999999,
    "text": "Matthias Schoenaerts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.4,
    "endTime": 90.86,
    "text": "Who's a director you'd love to work with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.86,
    "endTime": 92.26,
    "text": "Wes Anderson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.26,
    "endTime": 93.55000000000001,
    "text": "Would you ever love to direct?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.55,
    "endTime": 94.63,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.63,
    "endTime": 96.96,
    "text": "Who do you always love watching on screen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.96,
    "endTime": 98.264,
    "text": "Tilda Swinton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.264,
    "endTime": 99.67,
    "text": "What do you look for in a good script?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.8,
    "endTime": 104.67,
    "text": "I want to be surprised, but also satisfied."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.8,
    "endTime": 108.92,
    "text": "Do you have to be able to relate or like the character in order to play them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.92,
    "endTime": 110.33,
    "text": "I do, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.33,
    "endTime": 115.1,
    "text": "Comic book buffs, or historical experts, who are harder to please as audience members?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.1,
    "endTime": 116.3,
    "text": "They're both really tough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.3,
    "endTime": 117.1,
    "text": "I can imagine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.1,
    "endTime": 117.6,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.6,
    "endTime": 119.28899999999999,
    "text": "Favorite accent to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.29,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Brooklyn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.38,
    "text": "How do you practice accents?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.38,
    "endTime": 124.482,
    "text": "I find real life people on YouTube, then I just kind of mimic them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.482,
    "endTime": 125.49,
    "text": "Huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.49,
    "endTime": 127.539,
    "text": "Is there a moment on camera that has truly shaken you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.54,
    "endTime": 131.93,
    "text": "Yes. The scene I got to do with Saoirse Ronan in \"Mary Queen of Scots\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.93,
    "endTime": 133.733,
    "text": "What's your favorite scar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.4,
    "endTime": 136.55,
    "text": "This one. I got it when I was a little kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.55,
    "endTime": 137.79000000000002,
    "text": "Favorite book?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.3,
    "endTime": 139.42000000000002,
    "text": "Harry Potter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.42,
    "endTime": 141.1,
    "text": "Favorite artist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.1,
    "endTime": 142.1,
    "text": "Magritte."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.1,
    "endTime": 143.29999999999998,
    "text": "Favorite band?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.3,
    "endTime": 144.20000000000002,
    "text": "Favorite band?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.2,
    "endTime": 146.35,
    "text": "I mean, I have a lot, but ELO."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.35,
    "endTime": 147.4,
    "text": "Favorite song?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.4,
    "endTime": 149.287,
    "text": "Right now, \"The Oogum Boogum Song.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.287,
    "endTime": 152.18,
    "text": "Alright, well you picked a beautiful day for a gathering."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.18,
    "endTime": 154.16,
    "text": "What does a typical brunch entail?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.16,
    "endTime": 158.79999999999998,
    "text": "Uh, all the girls outside drinking and all the guys inside cooking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.8,
    "endTime": 160.98000000000002,
    "text": "What is your favorite cuisine to cook?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.98,
    "endTime": 163.67,
    "text": "I am not a good cook, but I can do a cheese board."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.67,
    "endTime": 164.503,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.503,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.0,
    "endTime": 167.45,
    "text": "What's your least favorite food to eat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.45,
    "endTime": 168.38,
    "text": "Taramasalata."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.38,
    "endTime": 169.1,
    "text": "Have you had that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.1,
    "endTime": 169.4,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.4,
    "endTime": 170.6,
    "text": "It's disgusting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.6,
    "endTime": 171.923,
    "text": "I'll try to stay away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.923,
    "endTime": 173.35,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.35,
    "endTime": 176.049,
    "text": "What's been the most rewarding project thus far in your career?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.05,
    "endTime": 177.09,
    "text": "I, Tonya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.09,
    "endTime": 178.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 181.92,
    "text": "Because I got to be a part of all the aspects of making that film."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.97,
    "endTime": 185.6,
    "text": "Producing or acting, which do you prefer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.6,
    "endTime": 190.14,
    "text": "I love producing, but acting will always be my big love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.14,
    "endTime": 191.95,
    "text": "What about producing did you not expect?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.95,
    "endTime": 193.28,
    "text": "Too much paperwork."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.28,
    "endTime": 194.22,
    "text": "Would you ever do theater?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.22,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 197.329,
    "text": "If you could make a documentary on any topic, what would it be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.33,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Why they shouldn't do oil drilling in the Great Australian Bight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 203.4,
    "text": "If you could cameo on any TV show, what would it be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.4,
    "endTime": 207.73000000000002,
    "text": "There's a wicked new show coming out on Hulu called Dollface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.73,
    "endTime": 209.709,
    "text": "It's a LuckyChap production."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.71,
    "endTime": 210.56,
    "text": "It's in the calendar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.56,
    "endTime": 213.81,
    "text": "True or false, you've played in a rugby league?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.81,
    "endTime": 215.46,
    "text": "No, false."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.46,
    "endTime": 216.91,
    "text": "I played on an ice hockey team."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.91,
    "endTime": 219.609,
    "text": "True or false, you tattooed your Suicide Squad cast?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.61,
    "endTime": 220.70000000000002,
    "text": "That's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.7,
    "endTime": 223.01899999999998,
    "text": "If I were to get a tattoo, what should I get and where?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.2,
    "endTime": 226.53,
    "text": "Two Salvador Dali elephants on your back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.53,
    "endTime": 227.95,
    "text": "That's specific."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.95,
    "endTime": 229.149,
    "text": "True or false for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.15,
    "endTime": 229.5,
    "text": "Shoot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.5,
    "endTime": 232.462,
    "text": "Did I offer you a glass of water and not give it to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.462,
    "endTime": 233.39,
    "text": "True."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.39,
    "endTime": 234.22199999999998,
    "text": "Sorry about that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.223,
    "endTime": 235.26000000000002,
    "text": "It's okay, Margot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.26,
    "endTime": 236.91,
    "text": "What's your favorite lip color?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.91,
    "endTime": 238.109,
    "text": "Chanel, Boy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.11,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Dead straight or natural wave hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.9,
    "endTime": 242.46,
    "text": "Natural wave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.46,
    "endTime": 244.47,
    "text": "What's an Australian beauty ritual that you follow every day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.47,
    "endTime": 245.67,
    "text": "Sunscreen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.67,
    "endTime": 247.29999999999998,
    "text": "What was the last piece of clothing that you bought?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.3,
    "endTime": 249.15,
    "text": "Bought a yellow t-shirt from Zimmermann."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.15,
    "endTime": 253.20000000000002,
    "text": "If you had to distill your peak signature style in one item of clothing, what would it be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.2,
    "endTime": 255.29999999999998,
    "text": "- High waisted pants. - Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.3,
    "endTime": 259.1,
    "text": "What would you say is your most extravagant and expensive outfit that you've ever worn?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.1,
    "endTime": 261.0,
    "text": "I feel like the dress I wore this year to the BAFTAs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.0,
    "endTime": 262.64,
    "text": "It was kind of extravagant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.64,
    "endTime": 264.13,
    "text": "Who's your favorite designer of all time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.13,
    "endTime": 265.21,
    "text": "Coco Chanel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.21,
    "endTime": 268.931,
    "text": "What's the most method that you've ever gotten for a role?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.931,
    "endTime": 275.35999999999996,
    "text": "I'm not really a method actor, but I do find myself unintentionally behaving like a character after a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.36,
    "endTime": 277.793,
    "text": "How did you prep to play Sharon Tate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.49,
    "endTime": 282.96000000000004,
    "text": "Lots of reading, watching a lot of films, spent time with people that knew her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.96,
    "endTime": 286.76,
    "text": "Um, and I always work with an acting coach, dialect coach, movement coach."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.76,
    "endTime": 291.71,
    "text": "- Queen Elizabeth, Harley Quinn, Tonya Harding, each requiring crazy physical makeovers. - Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.71,
    "endTime": 293.998,
    "text": "Is your prep process similar regardless of the character?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.999,
    "endTime": 295.15000000000003,
    "text": "The approach is similar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.15,
    "endTime": 302.29999999999995,
    "text": "The process always changes a little bit based on the character, but the approach is the same, and, inevitably, a lot of time in the hair and makeup chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.3,
    "endTime": 303.5,
    "text": "I can imagine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.5,
    "endTime": 308.143,
    "text": "And having played several people that actually existed, how does that influence your performance?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.16,
    "endTime": 318.3,
    "text": "Well, I always feel a sense of responsibility for a character, whether they're real or not, but definitely an added sense of responsibility when they are real life people, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.3,
    "endTime": 321.01,
    "text": "And you've played characters from so many different eras."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.01,
    "endTime": 323.88,
    "text": "If you can go back and live in any of those periods, which would it be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.0,
    "endTime": 326.6,
    "text": "The '60s."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.6,
    "endTime": 329.82000000000005,
    "text": "What's been the biggest positive change in Hollywood recently?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.82,
    "endTime": 331.01,
    "text": "Inclusivity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.01,
    "endTime": 333.43,
    "text": "What in the film world needs a drastic overhaul?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.5,
    "endTime": 337.01,
    "text": "Non-creatives making creative decisions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.01,
    "endTime": 340.159,
    "text": "Who's a voice in Hollywood that people should be listening to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.16,
    "endTime": 341.91,
    "text": "Women, all of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.91,
    "endTime": 344.92,
    "text": "What female performer is blowing your mind right now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.92,
    "endTime": 345.6,
    "text": "Phoebe Waller-Bridge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.6,
    "endTime": 346.76000000000005,
    "text": "Ah, love her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.76,
    "endTime": 348.4,
    "text": "- Hey, cool surfboard!  - Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.4,
    "endTime": 350.979,
    "text": "I imagine you're professional level at surfing, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.98,
    "endTime": 352.54,
    "text": "I am not a good surfer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.54,
    "endTime": 353.40000000000003,
    "text": "I just like doing it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.4,
    "endTime": 355.893,
    "text": "On a scale of one to ten, how good are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.893,
    "endTime": 357.69,
    "text": "A two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.69,
    "endTime": 360.0,
    "text": "Who has better beaches, Australia or California?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.0,
    "endTime": 360.8,
    "text": "Australia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.8,
    "endTime": 362.04,
    "text": "I knew you'd say that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.04,
    "endTime": 363.54,
    "text": "What's your go-to cocktail?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.54,
    "endTime": 364.0,
    "text": "G&T."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.0,
    "endTime": 365.73,
    "text": "What's your vice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.73,
    "endTime": 366.3,
    "text": "Ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.2,
    "endTime": 369.19,
    "text": "What's a fashion trend that you think will definitely come back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.68,
