    "text": "Chunky '80s earrings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.39,
    "endTime": 375.26,
    "text": "What is a fashion trend that you are positive will never grow old?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.22,
    "endTime": 377.8,
    "text": "Crisp white shirt, blue jeans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.8,
    "endTime": 381.84000000000003,
    "text": "And what's a fashion trend you think should never see the light of day ever again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.84,
