    "text": "Stripy toe socks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.99,
    "endTime": 385.79,
    "text": "I don't know if that was a thing here, but it was when I was a kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.79,
    "endTime": 387.0,
    "text": "Alright. So, where are you heading?"
