  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.643,
    "endTime": 427.29999999999995,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.3,
    "endTime": 429.0,
    "text": "Okay, last question I have for you, Margot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.0,
    "endTime": 432.03,
    "text": "I'm so excited for \"Once Upon a Time in Hollywood.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.03,
    "endTime": 433.91999999999996,
    "text": "What was it like working with Quentin Tarantino?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.91,
    "endTime": 436.55,
    "text": "It was the best ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.55,
    "endTime": 438.27000000000004,
    "text": "There are no cell phones on set."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.27,
    "endTime": 440.0,
    "text": "I don't think Quentin even owns one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.0,
    "endTime": 444.14,
    "text": "And every 100 rolls of film everyone stops, and has a drink, and celebrates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.14,
    "endTime": 447.63,
    "text": "I think you and I have a lot to celebrate right now, because we concluded our interview."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.63,
    "endTime": 448.96,
    "text": "I'll have a drink for the both of us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.96,
    "endTime": 450.219,
    "text": "Sounds good, Margot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.22,
